* 0.2 (2009-07-27)
 Nothing has been changed. Tested that this plugin is compatible with Rails 2.3.3.

* 0.2 (2009-02-21)
 Second release.
 Now the plugin can be used with Rails 2.1 and Rails 2.2 (I am not sure with Rails 2.0)
 Era based years(Wareki) can be displayed.
 distance_of_time_in_words method has been changed slightly. 
 
